      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLD REVOLVER (5) has a strong record this trip with three wins and three placings from seven starts. Hit the frame latest (19.95) when third at this track in a Grade 5. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. FROM THE DISCO (2) isn't a quick beginner but comes home hard, finishing out of the frame two back but did wind up strongly to place when third (25.26) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning 12 races. Expected to feature. SHORTY (4) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (25.02) at this track behind Swift Bree in a Grade 4/5. Has the pace to be prominent. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Hard to beat again. VISTA YTTRIUM (7) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance – sure to have admirers.",
